name: Paris under lockdown #2
description:
This photo was taken in Paris during the total lockdown of the city and the country following the COVID pandemic from March to May 2020.

This photo is the second of a series of 15 black and white photos of the empty streets of Paris taken with a digital pinhole camera made by myself and shows the Louvre pyramid seen from the arches of the Carousel.

The whole series is visible on my website at: https://samuelboivin.fr/stenope-lockdown/

Samuel Boivin
